creator: Hagen Quartett
description:
DECEMBER 24, 1992 | Mr. Halperin discussed the presidential pardon of former Secretary of Defense Caspar Weinberger and others involved in the Iran-Contra affair. He criticized the president’s actions, refuting the president’s comments that Secretary Weinberger was a patriot.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
title: Discussion: Iran-Contra Pardon and Law
